{
  "stem": "19218.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 195.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my father worked in-- in the forest, since this city was right on the outskirts of one of the largest forests in Poland called Puszcza Bialowieza.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And new industries started there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had the largest lumber mill in the country, which was happen to have been in that particular city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were a lot of new people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a small city, but it's like the pioneer towns where industry came in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Other people moved in in there, and my parents were one of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So after working for a while in the forest as a lumber hauler-- he was taking out the woods out of the forest onto the railroad tracks and from there it went to the mills-- he started thinking about going in business for himself.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he slowly build [BACKGROUND NOISE] a brick factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So since about 19-- I would say-- 29 or so, we were-- my father had a brick factory manufacturing bricks, not like they do it in here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, after watching the-- the movie and how the Jews worked in Egypt, this is exactly the picture which I remember how-- how this particular factory started, where the people-- people were actually stumping their feet on the clay and just mixing it to make it softer so they can-- so they can produce bricks.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And slowly, of course, progress even reached our little town, and they had a machine to do all the mixing of the clay and-- and instead of people doing it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and no electricity, but it was done with-- with horses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were-- they were going around in a circle, and-- and-- and-- and this is how he made his living in that town in there.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
